	   <tr><td colspan=2>Some ppl wondered about the 2nd lifetap, Ive noticed that there is a spell recovery time when you cant cast the same spell again right away so if you keep the 2 highest lifetaps up you can alternate between them faster...posibly the reasoning behind that...as for hot keys the input i wanted to give was that I rearanged my keyboard so my hotkeys are letters z x c v b n instead of 1 - 6 that makes it a little more comfortable for me rather than having to reach across the keyboard.<br><br>Kaydaver<br>Iksar Necro<br>Tunare<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
